texts.text: This page serves as a compact list of all unique particle textures which have ever existed in officially released versions of Minecraft. For an overview on when each texture was changed, see the appropriate History of textures subpages.
Note: the textures shown in this page are upscaled tenfold for display purposes.

2 Removed textures
Tinted particles have a pink background, untinted particles have a purple background.
